sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant MM_A as ModelMesh Pod A<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS + mTLS (opt)
    participant MM_B as ModelMesh Pod B<br/>8080/TCP Litelinks<br/>TLS + mTLS (opt)
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>8085/TCP or UDS<br/>plaintext
    participant etcd as etcd Cluster<br/>2379/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (configurable)
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(S3/PVC)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client, Storage: Flow 1: Inference Request (gRPC Proxy)
    Client->>MM_A: gRPC inference request<br/>mm-model-id or mm-vmodel-id header<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
    MM_A->>MM_A: Lookup model location<br/>(in-memory cache + etcd registry)
    alt Model on this pod
        MM_A->>Runtime: gRPC inference (zero-copy ByteBuf)<br/>ProtoSplicer injects model-id<br/>plaintext (localhost)
        Runtime-->>MM_A: Inference response
    else Model on another pod
        MM_A->>MM_B: Litelinks forward request<br/>Thrift over TCP 8080<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
        MM_B->>Runtime: gRPC inference (zero-copy ByteBuf)<br/>plaintext (localhost)
        Runtime-->>MM_B: Inference response
        MM_B-->>MM_A: Litelinks response<br/>Thrift 8080/TCP
    end
    MM_A-->>Client: gRPC inference response<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)

    Note over Client, Storage: Flow 2: Model Load on Cache Miss
    Client->>MM_A: gRPC inference for unloaded model
    MM_A->>etcd: Lookup model record<br/>gRPC 2379/TCP
    etcd-->>MM_A: Model metadata (path, type, size)
    MM_A->>Runtime: loadModel RPC<br/>gRPC 8085/TCP or UDS
    Runtime->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>IAM / access keys
    Storage-->>Runtime: Model artifacts
    Runtime-->>MM_A: Load complete (model size)
    MM_A->>etcd: Update model record (LOADED)<br/>gRPC 2379/TCP
    MM_A->>Runtime: Inference request<br/>gRPC plaintext
    Runtime-->>MM_A: Inference response
    MM_A-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client, Storage: Flow 3: VModel Transition (Blue-Green)
    Client->>MM_A: setVModel RPC<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP TLS
    MM_A->>etcd: Update vmodel record<br/>(set target model)
    MM_A->>Runtime: loadModel (new target)<br/>gRPC 8085/TCP or UDS
    Runtime->>Storage: Download new model<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP
    Storage-->>Runtime: Model artifacts
    Runtime-->>MM_A: Load complete
    MM_A->>etcd: Promote target to active<br/>(atomic switch)
    MM_A-->>Client: setVModel response<br/>(zero-downtime transition)
